yle=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"90973829bc64dfed33756fafa42a9d6062f25933","tid":1566263,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce5ac9c97f81b1c2f63443f2ce64d879d4343aa5","tid":1566263,"uid":183675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唱歌表面上係團結</span></strong></span><br />\n大家出商場唱歌嗰陣都覺得香港人團結<br />\n但係呢個只係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">假象</span></span><br />\n我哋嘅主線俾大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">忽略咗</span></span><br />\n915遊行冇人提 冇人開 po<br />\n大家相比於以往三個月<br />\n無團結到不特只<br />\n仲變成一盤散沙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家唔好輸比國際戰線睇！<br />\n香港人一直以來都係咁團結</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">915 銅鑼灣遊行</span></strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一個都不能少</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92H4rHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92H4rHT.jpg&h=df5da75e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"【終極核彈】《願榮光》之後－成立海外臨時民主政府<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566796</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》之後。。。<br />\n天滅中共 平反六四！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海外臨時政府 自由香港<br />\nFREE HONG KONG</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/freehongkonghkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreehongkonghkg&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88i%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=f9c54c2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"f37265c9b3ddf142af8a46c3be2a632233ca6d0e","tid":1566263,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d842844bbb703ee4e64cc6e1b0bc9f93a846a25","tid":1566263,"uid":183675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"唔好輸比人睇！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/usa-help-request-china-government-dismiss-carrie-lam-and-her-team-let-john-tsang-chun-wah-be-next-chief-executive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fusa-help-request-china-government-dismiss-carrie-lam-and-her-team-let-john-tsang-chun-wah-be-next-chief-executive&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88i%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=99e26c4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/usa-help-request-china-government-dismiss-carrie-lam-and-he